WEBVTT

00:05.081 --> 00:07.988
The Olympics is the biggest sporting event on the planet.

00:08.553 --> 00:11.304
Sports allow us to open our mind to many values,...

00:11.651 --> 00:13.682
...including the essential values of Olympism...

00:14.035 --> 00:16.720
...which are excellence, respect and friendship.

00:19.294 --> 00:20.867
Living the Olympic values.

00:20.965 --> 00:27.853
In the name of all competitors, I promise that we shall take part in these Youth Olympic Games,...

00:28.087 --> 00:30.427
...in the true spirit of sportsmanship,...

00:30.908 --> 00:32.783
...for the glory of sports.

